Thai
.author
Alan Kent 
.source
Includes source in C.
.description
A simple Thai quiz program developed by the author while he was learning
the Thai language.  It loads complete Thai sentences and words from a
supplied file.  If you click on the sentence or word gadget the program
will pick a random sentence/word.  You then click on the
Thai/Speak/Phonetic/English gadget to display that version (or speak it).  
